{"tid":857413,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不停係街撞見 係咁岩定係緣份？","createTime":"2018-10-11T05:33:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T05:53:25.000Z","uid":209405,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4e46d0db3ede3cf9d60342e23fc9d5b2a0466cf6","tid":857413,"uid":209405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T05:33:08.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我同前度散左兩年 <br />\n其實我一早已經放低左<br />\n但呢兩年我一直都時不時諗起佢<br />\n會默默咁關注佢 <br />\n有時會睇佢ig 見到佢過得好我會有種安心感<br />\n<br />\n但總係會有啲時候 會特別想搵番佢<br />\n會有幾日好想wtsapp佢 但冷靜落泥就冇事<br />\n繼續各有各生活<br />\n<br />\n大半年前有日行mk 突然有種好強烈嘅會撞到佢<br />\n跟住唔洗十分鐘就真係街上同佢迎面撞正<br />\n我嗰下唔識俾反應 笑左笑就走左<br />\n<br />\n跟住前幾日 執房摷番晒啲舊相同埋愛情遺物出泥<br />\n接住幾日個腦都係佢 <br />\n然後我琴日行cwb 行行下宜傢又同佢迎面撞正<br />\n我嗰下心跳快左跳 腳都有啲軟 <br />\n我同行個fd都見到佢 <br />\n行過左之後問我 嗰個係咪..?<br />\n<br />\n我不停咁問自己 其實呢啲係叫咁岩 定係 緣份？<br />\n念念不忘 係咪真係必有迴響？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbdef510b6b85a0185e3ef4bdb3138544d9f93b0","tid":857413,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T05:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374cbdfd09d93e7b5bca997e4087e274cabe86f4","tid":857413,"uid":38383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T05:34:12.000Z","msg":"腳軟係因為諗起比佢屌屎忽?"},{"pid":"f7cbd19117deb2e9f06506971aad04e2a2be4c1e","tid":857413,"uid":209405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"374cbdfd09d93e7b5bca997e4087e274cabe86f4","tid":857413,"uid":38383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T05:34:12.000Z","msg":"腳軟係因為諗起比佢屌屎忽?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T05:36:12.000Z","msg":"唔係 純粹係因為太緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\